Also the bg was fun, simple but effective ^^

Thanks for spending time to look :)

node.text:
I had a lot of fun drawing Hu Tao! She's one of my favourite characters! I love her personality and appearance a lot 🦋

I hope you like my depiction of her. I am getting more and more confident with drawing girls ^^

I also included my sketch here. It's a rather clean sketch for me😅 

Wish you a pleasant day~

node.text:
Here's the finished Xiao drawing in a modern setting with a sukajan jacket. I saw an article on pixiv featuring drawings with those jackets and I immediately saw Xiao in one of them.

That idea isn't new at all and when I started drawing I noticed many had done it before me. But that's fine ^^ I just wanted to mention that, and @/ hydedraws for their idea, I guess I subconsciously had their design in mind as well. It's really cool!

Hope you like it! 😊

🌊 Who would you like to see next?

node.text:
I finally managed to finish this drawing of Yoimiya!

✨It's been a while since I last drew a female character.
It made me insecure to post and draw them since people don't know me for this content. As much as I enjoyed it, the feedback was always less than for my male characters. So I was hesitant posting this. But I finally did and the encouragement and nice words I received so far have been amazing 🖤😊 thank you so much! I hope you like it ^^

#yoimiya #yoimiyagenshinimpact #genshinfanart #genshinimpact #genshinimpactfanart #genshinimpactart #girldrawing #原神 #digitalillustration #digitaldrawing #clipstudiopaint #mangadrawing #inazuma

node.text:
I made another eye study! I did this last year and noticed it helps me to identify how I want to draw eyes. And since it changes over time I wanted to redo it and try many different styles to get inspired for my own work.

I also borrowed kamochiruus and zumizumi0126 art style, I hope you don't mind 😌

👀 Hope you like it, it was a lot of fun and I highly encourage you to try it as well when you're art blocked or bored :)

#eyedrawing #eyestudy #artstudy #eyepainting #digitalart #eyestyle #animeeyes #animeeye #eyememe #digitaldrawing #animeartstyle #clipstudiopaint  #artstyles #szainx_support

🍁Will you wish for him?

node.text:
Hi!
Since some people asked me how I shade hair, I wanted to make a quick "tutorial" for it 😊

❗Disclaimer: Note that this is just my way (one of many) to do that. Not even I stick to this and I change it as I need it.

So I hope this helps you a bit and gives you an insight of my process :)

I hope you have fun!

🍤 Feel free to comment if you have any questions or feedback!

#arttutorial #digitalart #stepbystep #artwip #howtodraw #howtodrawhair #drawinghair #animestyle #coloringtutorial #drawingtips #paintingtips #drawingtutorial #arthelp #arttips
